<item>
            <title>[LU-3282] copy_and_ioctl() uses wrong pointer in call to obd_iocontrol()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3282</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In copy_and_ioctl() the userspace pointer is diligently copied in to kernel space but then passed to obd_iocontrol() as the karg pointer.  This creates a minor DoS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
